 remembering there's as far as even as far as cultures go on the common everyday level.

00:19:51.780 --> 00:19:57.300
 There's all kinds of customs of what's appropriate or inappropriate in human culture,

00:19:57.300 --> 00:20:05.700
 you know, and this is in no way to kind of denigrate whatever any, any individuals kind of

